{"arkId":"cl010104331","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104331","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre astronomique","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre astronomique"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1650","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1650,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Vautier, Louis","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1590","place":"Blois","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1638","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7023","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre astronomique ; bo\u00eetier en cristal de roche pr\u00e9sentant quatre lobes interrompus par des pointes triangulaires. Couvercle et fond maintenus par des armatures en laiton grav\u00e9. Pendant \u00e0 l\u0027aspect d\u0027un chapiteau \u00e0 feuilles d\u0027acanthe ; bouton moulur\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u0027oppos\u00e9. De bas en haut du cadran apparaissent les indications suivantes : le jour accompagn\u00e9 du nom et du signe de la plan\u00e8te lui correspondant ; l\u0027\u00e2ge et les phases de la lune ; les heures ; le quanti\u00e8me du mois. Disque mobile central grav\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris ; pourtour pareillement grav\u00e9 et orn\u00e9 d\u0027Amours personnifiant les quatre \u00e9l\u00e9ments. Mouvement ajust\u00e9 dans la bo\u00eete, muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre et d\u0027une fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet ajour\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux fleuris. Piliers en forme de balustre.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Loys Vautier\/A Bloys [signature ponctu\u00e9e d\u0027une fleurette]","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,5","displayDimension":"7,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4,3","displayDimension":"4,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,5","displayDimension":"2,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau :","placeOfCreation":"Blois (Centre-\u003ELoir-et-Cher = Loir et Cher)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"},{"value":"Louis XIV (1643-1